<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Your Website Name</title>
    <style>
        /* Base Reset */
        * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }

        /* Navigation */
        nav { background: #333; color: #fff; padding: 1rem; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
        nav ul { list-style: none; display: flex; }
        nav ul li { margin-left: 20px; }
        nav a { color: #fff; text-decoration: none; }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero { 
            background: #f4f4f4; 
            padding: 100px 20px; 
            text-align: center; 
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .hero h1 { font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
        .hero p { font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; max-width: 600px; }
        .btn { background: #ff4a57; color: #fff; padding: 10px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; }

        /* Features Section (Responsive Grid) */
        .features { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; padding: 50px 20px; justify-content: center; }
        .feature-box { flex: 1 1 300px; margin: 15px; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px; }

        /* Footer */
        footer { background: #333; color: #fff; text-align: center; padding: 20px 0; margin-top: 20px; }

        /* Responsive Breakpoint for Mobile */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            nav { flex-direction: column; }
            nav ul { margin-top: 1rem; padding: 0; }
            .hero h1 { font-size: 2rem; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav>
        <div class="logo"><strong>MyBrand</strong></div>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="#">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">Services</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">Contact</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>

    <header class="hero">
        <h1>Modern Solutions for You</h1>
        <p>This is a fully responsive landing page. Shrink your browser window to see how the layout adapts for mobile users.</p>
        <a href="#" class="btn">Get Started</a>
    </header>

    <section class="features">
        <div class="feature-box">
            <h3>Responsive Design</h3>
            <p>Layouts that work on any screen size using CSS Flexbox.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-box">
            <h3>Fast Performance</h3>
            <p>Clean HTML5 and CSS3 code for quick loading times.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-box">
            <h3>SEO Optimized</h3>
            <p>Proper semantic tags to help search engines find you.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 Your Company Name. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
